  "lifecycle_summary": "DiscoverEvidence iterates over fact envelopes, builds a per-repo content index via buildEvidenceContentIndex, then routes each envelope to the appropriate extractor based on artifact_type and file path. Each extractor calls matchCatalog which checks candidate strings against CatalogEntry.Aliases. Resolved evidence is deduplicated with a seen map. Resolve then groups EvidenceFact values into Candidate buckets, applies Assertion overrides and rejections, filters by confidenceThreshold, and returns both the candidate list and the promoted ResolvedRelationship slice.",
